item.title: AMD
item.description: score:28 Chances: AMD acquires French AI software company Mipsology, showcasing innovation and growth in partnerships. AMD showcases continued enterprise data center momentum with EPYC CPUs and Pensando DPUs. New AMD Radeon RX graphics cards deliver high-performance gaming experiences, potentially driving sales. AMD strengthens Amazon’s EC2 instances with EPYC processors, expanding its market presence.
